p: Túlio De Lima Campos, Ricardo Durães-Carvalho, Gabriel Luz Wallau, and Lindomar José Pena designed the study. Túlio De Lima Campos, Ricardo Durães-Carvalho, Antonio Mauro Rezende, Otávio Valério de Carvalho, Gabriel Luz Wallau, Alain Kohl, and Lindomar José Pena analyzed the data. Túlio De Lima Campos, Ricardo Durães-Carvalho, Antonio Mauro Rezende, Otávio Valério de Carvalho, Gabriel Luz Wallau, Alain Kohl, and Lindomar José Pena wrote the paper.
